<main class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4" aria-label="404 — Page not found"><div class="max-w-xl text-center w-full"><p class="bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-br dark:from-blue-500 dark:to-indigo-400 dark:via-blue-400 font-extrabold from-blue-600 leading-none select-none sm:text-[10rem] text-[8rem] text-transparent to-indigo-500 tracking-tighter via-blue-500" aria-hidden="true">404</p><h1 class="dark:text-white font-bold mt-4 sm:text-3xl text-2xl text-gray-900">Page not found</h1><p class="dark:text-gray-400 max-w-md mt-3 mx-auto text-base text-gray-500">The page you&#39;re looking for doesn&#39;t exist or has been moved.</p><div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 items-center justify-center mt-8"><a href="/" class="bg-blue-600 dark:bg-blue-500 dark:focus-visible:ring-blue-400 dark:hover:bg-blue-400 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-blue-500 font-semibold gap-2 hover:bg-blue-500 inline-flex items-center motion-reduce:duration-0 motion-reduce:transition-none px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-sm text-white transition-colors"><span>Go to homepage</span><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path></svg></a> <button type="button" data-tc-go-back class="bg-white border border-gray-300 dark:bg-gray-800 dark:border-gray-600 dark:focus-visible:ring-gray-500 dark:hover:bg-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-gray-400 font-semibold gap-2 hover:bg-gray-50 inline-flex items-center motion-reduce:duration-0 motion-reduce:transition-none px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg shadow-sm text-gray-700 text-sm transition-colors"><svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18"></path></svg><span>Go back</span></button></div></div></main><script nonce="">
		if (!window.tcGoBackAttached) {
